[32m│[0m `<math>`, `<noscript>`, `<b>`, `<p>`, `<button>`, `<canvas>`, `<xss>`,       [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m `<custom>`, `<datalist>`, `<output>`                                         [32m│[0m
